# Project Structure

This is a Flask-based platform for dataset sharing and analysis, allowing users to upload, share, and visualize datasets.

## Main Entry Points

- [run.py](mdc:run.py) - Application entry point, responsible for starting the Flask server
- [app/__init__.py](mdc:app/__init__.py) - Application initialization file containing the Flask application factory function and blueprint registration
- [app/config.py](mdc:app/config.py) - Contains application configuration options

## Project Modules

- `app/auth/` - User authentication functionality
- `app/dashboard/` - Data dashboard functionality
- `app/datasets/` - Dataset management functionality
- `app/visualization/` - Data visualization functionality
- `app/sharing/` - Dataset sharing functionality
- `app/api/` - API endpoints
- `app/scout_analysis/` - Scout report analysis module

## Data Models

- [app/models/user.py](mdc:app/models/user.py) - User model
- [app/models/dataset.py](mdc:app/models/dataset.py) - Dataset model
- [app/models/share.py](mdc:app/models/share.py) - Sharing settings model


